gobblin.data.management.conversion.hive.entities

Class QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.conversion.hive.entities.QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity

  • public class QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity
extends Object
    Represents a gobblin Record in the Hive avro to orc conversion flow. The HiveConvertExtractor extracts exactly one QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity. This class is a container for all metadata about a HiveTable or a HivePartition needed to build the hive conversion query.The gobblin task constructs can mutate this object as it get passed from Extractor to Converters.
    • The HiveConvertExtractor creates QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity using the HiveRegistrationUnit in the workunit
    • The AbstractAvroToOrcConverter builds the QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity#query using QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity#hiveUnitSchema.
    • The HiveQueryExecutionWriter executes the hive query at QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity#getConversionQuery()
